arts.ttl: Oldham thrash Halifax to set up York play-off semi-final showdown
Eliminator Preview: Oldham Athletic v FC Halifax Town
arts.sum: Oldham Athletic were one of the fancied sides when things got underway back in August and quickly cemented their place in the top seven. The Shaymen have been beaten at this stage in three of the last five seasons while Micky Mellon will be hoping for a repeat of his two previous National League play-off triumphs with Tranmere Rovers (2018) and Fleetwood Town (2010).
